content: [2025, Age 22] [TextBlock(text="Wow, the tech scene in Japan was eye-opening, from their AI-driven cafes to the way they integrate tech into everyday life. Makes me wonder how we can bring that innovation back to NYC. Gotta say, my time there has definitely shifted my perspective on what's possible.", type='text')]

[TextBlock(text="Spent the last few days diving into Rust, a language I've been meaning to learn. Pairing with AI has made the learning curve less daunting. Every line of code feels like a step towards something bigger. Excited to see where this skill takes me next.", type='text')]
